data.description: *REDUCED* Stunning tree studded 2.4+/- acres nestled in the heart of Hill Country! Property features include trophy oak trees, enchanting seasonal creek and complete serenity. Privately located at the end of the road, this property offers all the benefits of ranch living without the maintenance. Majestic deer, turkey and fox are regular visitors of the property. Electricity and a water in are conveniently at the road. There are numerous homesites that would encompass both wooded and long-range views. Gated community, low HOA. Hi-speed internet available. Additional acreage available. Motivated Seller!
